    <item>
      <title>佐治亚州立法者无视抗议通过“外国代理人”法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/georgia-lawmakers-pass-foreign-agent-law-defying-protesters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚立法者通过了一项反对所谓外国影响的法案，尽管数千人在议会外抗议，反对西方盟友称该措施类似于俄罗斯用来镇压异见的法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/georgia-lawmakers-pass-foreign-agent-law-defying-protesters</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 12:51:32 GMT</pubDate>
